OL,3,CHuman remains found in river in search
OL,4,Cfor missing teenager
OL,6,FFormal identification is yet to take
OL,7,Fplace, but Devon and Cornwall Police
OL,8,Fhas said that the family of 15-year-
OL,9,Fold Taylor Charlton have been informed
OL,10,Fand are being supported by specialist
OL,11,Fofficers.
OL,13,FThe last confirmed sighting of Taylor
OL,14,Fis on CCTV near a footpath close to
OL,15,FTarka Leisure Centre and the Seven
OL,16,FBrethren car park, in Barnstaple, at
OL,17,F10.41pm on Friday 8 May. He is seen
OL,18,Fheading in the direction of the River
OL,19,FTaw.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
