CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F403A1782400702
OL,3,CHuman remains found in river in search
OL,4,Cfor missing teenager
OL,6,FA 20-year-old man was arrested on
OL,7,Fsuspicion of murder on 12 June but was
OL,8,Flater released on bail until September
OL,9,Fpending further enquiries.
OL,11,FThe police has said that Taylor's
OL,12,Ffamily is being supported by
OL,13,Fspecialist officers.
OL,15,FDevon and Cornwall Police said: "We
OL,16,Fask that their privacy is respected at
OL,17,Fthis time.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
